  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Frame agreement with NGO (Fida Int.)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Empowering Partners for Social Responsibility. The project aims to increase the capacity of a local partner to do holistic development work in local communities. Nepal is one of the poorest countries in the world_ where majority of the people live in rural areas. Fida&#xE2;&#x80;&#x99;s partner in Nepal is the Assemblies of God church (AOG). The project provides training and awareness-raising for the partner on a great variety of issues related to development work. Fida and AOG work together in the local communities and through this hands-on development work the partner acquires practical skills. The project focuses on three major components: Literacy_ Community Health Education (CHE) and HIV/AIDS. As AOG&#xE2;&#x80;&#x99;s skills and knowledge grow_ the partner will become increasingly capable of doing effective community development work of its own. This will contribute to the increasing impact of the partner&#xE2;&#x80;&#x99;s work at community level.</narrative>
  </description>
